From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 12:36:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 04/21] UPSTREAM: DP: Remove some of the excess parameters in
 rx path

Remove the following excess parameters in rx path :
peer mac addr ,is_4addr_sta ,is_drop_packet & no_8023_flag
from hal_rx_desc_data

Patch-dependency : None

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
